ing fires at the right threshold\n- Policy head initial weight scale is small\n- Categorical constructed from logits (not probs)\n- Truncated episodes correctly mark done\n- Advantage normalization edge cases\n- Minibatch plan with small/large batch sizes\n- No weight decay in optimizer\n- Rollout health counter accumulation\n\n## Wave plans\n\nAdded design docs for four waves under `wave/`:\n- **first-light 02-05**: single-agent env wrapper, observation cleanup, verification ladder, auxiliary prediction heads\n- **architecture**: attention re-intro, LSTM memory, observation pipeline optimization\n- **self-play**: opponent pool, cycling detection, evaluation harness\n- **scale**: decoupled actor/learner, game-theoretic training (NFSP)"
